| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4014 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d5a3cd7d-4293-5117-9258-974b37ba5cb7"
